snippet.title: The Lost City of Atlantis gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for The Lost City of Atlantis, Dos PC game produced by Noch Software in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/lost-city-of-atlantis-the/8558/
The Lost City of Atlantis is a very nice game, action, platformer, puzzle based. It is an interesting game in which you get the more action on land and in water.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
